            "title": "A股跌轉升   創板升近3.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股跌轉升，深股升逾2%，創板半日升近3.5%，成交13687.21億元 (人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指半日收升13點或0.35%，報3778點，今早開報44365點，平開，最低見3765點，跌20點或0.53%，即反覆向上，最高報3782，升17點或0.45%，半日成交5740.32億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日升244點或2.01%，報12362點，今早開報12140，升22點或0.18%，早段低見12085，跌33點或0.27%，後段高見12397，升279點或2.3%，半日成交7946.89億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日收升0.88%或38點，今早開報4365，平開。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日升96點或3.48%，報2872點，今早開報2793，升17點或0.54%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15233145-a%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e8%bd%89%e5%8d%87-%e5%89%b5%e6%9d%bf%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%913-5",
